dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from https://geo.gob.bo. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS:
1. Created and populated reference name field. 2. Created and populated Admin0 name and p-code fields. 3. Found and fixed 1 gap error and 2 overlap errors. 4. Constructed Admin1 p-codes by appending ISO code "BO". 5. Added missing island feature from Admin3 "Salinas de Garcí Mendoza". 6. Found and fixed 1 multipart sliver error.
